name: The Printers Inc
tag_list: photography, photos, social, social-media, ecommerce, printing, art, design, creative
overview:
The Printers Inc is a UK based startup that provides e-commerce and print-on-demand solutions to artists and photographers. Their first product (The Button Factory) generates HTML widgets and plugins to enable individuals to sell across the web and social media.

The Button Factory generates embeddable HTML plugins and widgets to allow artists to sell their artwork from any website or blog within 5 minutes for free. The Button Factory also gives users complete control over their own margins, as well as detailed analytics about button performance and has the ability to integrate into any digital presence be it a blog, website or photo-sharing social network.
